description:
What do animals do in the spring of their lives? They mate! Wildly!

Four mischievous friends have met their match: their own hearts! Now that they're older, the only troubles these country boys find make them moan and pant. Kou-chan wants to confess to Kishi, but he's full of heart-pounding doubt over Kishi's response. Mitsuru, the serious boy pining for a lost love, is ambushed by Tarou, an obtuse, air-headed sadist, full of devotion for his darling. And who is this tall boy, beating everyone up yet shooting flowers out of the panels? Somebody needs to figure out his body language.

Psyche Delico comes out to play... all over the pages of PURE LOVE'S SEXY TIME!

Story Titles

  • Prologue of Love in a Small Town
  • Love is Destined Act. 1
  • Love is Destined Act. 2
  • Love is Destined Act. 3
  • Mating Sexy Time
  • First Friend Act. 1
  • First Friend Act. 2
  • Epilogue of Love in a Small Town
name: Vol. 1

description:
They may be in relationships and having sex, but boys at puberty have a lot of problems to solve!

The long-awaited sequel to the fan favorite series Pure Love’s Sexy Time is here! Kou gets frustrated with Kishi for being too gentle with him, Satoshi and Eishou have trouble finding a way to walk the same path to their futures and there isn’t enough verbal communication between Tarou and Mitsuru while they become more and more physically compatible… Where will these boys’ paths lead them?! The final conclusion to a Pure Love’s Sexy Time.
name: Vol. 2

description: The Afterburner Team is back! Meet Persephone, Goddess of Fertility and discover her pact with Hades. Also in this issue we meet Ezekiel Daring..The Greatest Adventurer of all Space and Time! Action, Science Fiction Noir and classic good girl art--just as you like it.
name: Tachyon Shuffle

description:
All The King's Men

Who can you really trust? We live in a world where politicians spin intricate webs of lies as a part of their job description. But nobody is prepared for what happens when those lies are more dangerous than anyone could have imagined.

Lucas, who served with Carmen's deceased boyfriend in the U.S Marine Corps, goes AWOL, forced by dark secrets to retreat to the relative safety of his family farm in Kansas.
name: All The King's Men

description:
The guardians of the forest have spoken.

Despite their doubts, they have agreed to share their wisdom with Orgot, so that he can finally unveil the truth behind the constant raids on Ninev.

Meanwhile, Farian faces his own and peculiar challenges without noticing the mysterious shadow that follows him at a distance.

Will the adventurers find the answers they seek beneath the forgotten ruins of Lebania?'

Howling Moon Part 2

Werewolves and zombies fighting to the death! A rotting gumshoe mummy searching for answers. The strange and unusual tale of Dick Mummy, the undead detective, continues in the second part of the Howling Moon three part mystery!
name: Howling Moon Part 2

The Cruel Dance Music of the Universe -Part 1

Government spending cuts cause a top secret project to be shutdown... Unwittingly causing said project to open up an extra-dimensional portal that rips open the fabric of space-time and unleases 3-eyed purple apes (Who have an interest in the stock market) upon the known universe. (Or... Something like that.)
name: The Cruel Dance Music of the Universe - Part 1

description: Robyn competes for the crystal and makes a deal with the King. Final part of the Double Dead series.

Everyone is Someone's Fetish is the fourth volume of Finn and Charlie Are Hitched, and the first in full color!

Finn and Charlie Are Hitched is a weekly slice-of-life comic about a gay couple-Finn and Charlie, who are married-and their friends. There's Candy, who has just become reacquainted with the daughter she gave up for adoption 22 years ago, Krys. There's Corey, a young gay man trying to figure out who he wants to be, and his on-again, off-again indie-rock boyfriend, Ken, who has become Krys's best friend. There's Finn's neurotic brother Gus, and there's Nina and Mike and their two kids, the very manic Katie, and their special-needs toddler, Bennie.
name: Everyone is Someone's Fetish

description:
Fantastic Sunday - A group of four friends hang out at the beach until a big angry kid starts to ruin everyone's fun.

Uaah! - An unhappy baby doesn't give his parents any rest, not letting them get a single night's sleep. The only one who seems to calm him down is his pretty babysitter.
name: Fantastic Sunday; Uaah!
